data.description: Recently remodeled home is move in ready! Kitchen with Quartz counters ,new cabinets and stainless steel appliances. Bathrooms with new fixtures and ceramic tile. Finished family room with hearth in the lower level. New light fixtures. Enclosed 3 season porch with new windows. Newer heating system. Circular driveway. One acre lot. Conservation land across street. Short distance to walking trails. Close to shopping and major highways. Less than 12 miles to Manchester airport.
